1997;;Northern Lights;;American;;Linda Yellen;;Diane Keaton;;family;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Lights_(1997_film);;Childless widow Roberta (Diane Keaton) receives news of the death of her estranged brother. Upon arriving in her hometown for her brother's funeral, Roberta receives an unexpected inheritance, her nine-year-old nephew Jack (Joseph Cross). Savvy and curious, Jack and Roberta struggle to find common ground.